{"tid":147494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《每日鏡報》投票調查，30%廠迷仍然支持雲加","createTime":"2017-03-08T01:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T01:53:07.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9e06e0f7d5b300f10b21a479be6ca799d9bef4","tid":147494,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"《每日鏡報》在比賽結束後立刻進行了一項「雲加應該怎麼辦的調查？」截止目前已經有1.2萬人參與投票，其中50%的投票者選擇「夏季走人」，30%的投票者選擇「留下」，還有20%的投票者選擇了「立刻走人」。<br />\n雖然雲加不太可能選擇立刻辭職，但是僅剩下30%的人支持他留任，一場慘敗過後，雲加要贏回球迷的信任，道阻且長。"},{"pid":"665792c43a802fc4ec1799a67ddb70d5abb6fad1","tid":147494,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"僅你老母"},{"pid":"ca4f5ae4a9d6148ba95fdc451f40c21a072da600","tid":147494,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:40:02.000Z","msg":"50%支持雲加走人<br />\n淨低嗰50%支持雲加即刻死"},{"pid":"5b444eb0b78590f29da621ac9aed4c4b04b65b1d","tid":147494,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50%支持雲加走人<br />\n淨低嗰50%支持雲加即刻死</blockquote><br />\n反雲反雲連眼都盲埋"},{"pid":"c62114dbb89c0e1b75bafe7f2be427ca8a59d86a","tid":147494,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>50%支持雲加走人<br />\n淨低嗰50%支持雲加即刻死</blockquote><br />\n反雲反到連眼都盲埋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"edd9cc9d5f4805b3a785ef2718b3dd69a310e4c6","tid":147494,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50%支持雲加走人<br />\n淨低嗰50%支持雲加即刻死</blockquote><br />\n文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"e4c13e855fb126e4972142b4ac697a704a0a38b9","tid":147494,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>50%支持雲加走人<br />\n淨低嗰50%支持雲加即刻死</blockquote><br />\n反雲反到連眼都盲埋</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我咁講啫